{"id":474003,"url":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_G._Avildsen","text":"John Guilbert Avildsen (December 21, 1935 \u2013 June 16, 2017) was an American movie director. He won the Academy Award for Best Director in 1977 for \"Rocky\".\nOther movie he directed include \"Joe\", \"Save the Tiger\", \"Fore Play\", \"The Formula\", \"Neighbors\", \"For Keeps\", \"Lean on Me\", \"The Power of One\", \"8 Seconds\", \"Inferno\", \"Rocky V\" and the first three \"Karate Kid\" movies.\nAvildsen died on June 16, 2017 in Los Angeles, California of pancreatic cancer, aged 81.","categories":[],"infobox_types":[],"annotations":[{"uri":"Americans","surface_form":"American","offset":66},{"uri":"Movie_director","surface_form":"movie director","offset":75},{"uri":"Academy_Award_for_Best_Director","surface_form":"Academy Award for Best Director","offset":102},{"uri":"Rocky","surface_form":"Rocky","offset":147},{"uri":"Joe_(1970_movie)","surface_form":"Joe","offset":188},{"uri":"Save_the_Tiger","surface_form":"Save the Tiger","offset":195},{"uri":"Fore_Play","surface_form":"Fore Play","offset":213},{"uri":"The_Formula_(1980_movie)","surface_form":"The Formula","offset":226},{"uri":"Neighbors_(1981_movie)","surface_form":"Neighbors","offset":241},{"uri":"For_Keeps_(movie)","surface_form":"For Keeps","offset":254},{"uri":"Lean_on_Me_(movie)","surface_form":"Lean on Me","offset":267},{"uri":"The_Power_of_One_(movie)","surface_form":"The Power of One","offset":281},{"uri":"8_Seconds","surface_form":"8 Seconds","offset":301},{"uri":"Inferno_(1999_movie)","surface_form":"Inferno","offset":314},{"uri":"Rocky_V","surface_form":"Rocky V","offset":325},{"uri":"The_Karate_Kid_(1984_movie)","surface_form":"Karate Kid","offset":355},{"uri":"Los_Angeles","surface_form":"Los Angeles","offset":409},{"uri":"California","surface_form":"California","offset":422},{"uri":"Pancreatic_cancer","surface_form":"pancreatic cancer","offset":436}]}